{"comments":"Unified GPU Rendering Target with Automatic Fallback\n\nThis module provides a unified interface for GPU-accelerated rendering\nwith automatic fallback based on browser capabilities:\n\n```\nWebGPU (iOS 17+, Chrome 113+)\n   ↓ fallback\nWebGL2 (iOS 15+, Chrome 56+)\n   ↓ fallback\nCanvas2D (all browsers)\n```\n\n## Usage\n\n```purescript\nimport Hydrogen.Target.GPU as GPU\n\nmain :: Effect Unit\nmain = do\n  GPU.detectCapabilities >>= \\caps -> do\n    Console.log $ \"Best backend: \" <> show caps.bestBackend\n    Console.log $ \"WebGPU: \" <> show caps.webgpu\n    Console.log $ \"WebGL2: \" <> show caps.webgl2\n    Console.log $ \"Canvas2D: \" <> show caps.canvas2d\n\n  GPU.createRenderer \"my-canvas\" >>= case _ of\n    Left err -> Console.log $ \"Error: \" <> err\n    Right renderer -> do\n      GPU.render renderer commands\n      GPU.dispose renderer\n```\n\n## Performance Characteristics\n\n| Backend  | Particles | Complex Effects | 3D | Browser Support |\n|----------|-----------|-----------------|----|--------------------|\n| WebGPU   | 1M+       | Full            | Yes| iOS 17+, Chrome 113+|\n| WebGL2   | 100K+     | Partial         | Yes| iOS 15+, Chrome 56+ |\n| Canvas2D | 1K        | Limited         | No | All browsers       |\n","declarations":[{"children":[],"comments":"GPU capabilities detection result.\n","info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"typeSynonym","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Record"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["webgpu",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Boolean"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["webgl2",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Boolean"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["canvas2d",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Boolean"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["bestBackend",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Target","GPU"],"Backend"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"tag":"REmpty"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[111,4],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Target/GPU.purs","start":[106,1]},"title":"GPUCapabilities"},{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[101,11],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Target/GPU.purs","start":[101,3]},"title":"WebGPU"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[102,11],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Target/GPU.purs","start":[102,3]},"title":"WebGL2"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[103,13],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Target/GPU.purs","start":[103,3]},"title":"Canvas2D"}],"comments":"Available rendering backends in order of preference.\n","info":{"dataDeclType":"data","declType":"data","roles":[],"typeArguments":[]},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[103,13],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Target/GPU.purs","start":[100,1]},"title":"Backend"},{"children":[],"comments":"Detect available GPU capabilities.\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Effect"],"Effect"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Target","GPU"],"GPUCapabilities"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[114,45],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Target/GPU.purs","start":[114,1]},"title":"detectCapabilities"},{"children":[],"comments":"Get the best available backend.\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Effect"],"Effect"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Target","GPU"],"Backend"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[126,33],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Target/GPU.purs","start":[126,1]},"title":"getBestBacke